{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id27f3a56d-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419","identifier":"/us/usc/t45/s1115"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1115"},"text":"§ 1115.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Redemption of stock","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For the purpose of computing the amount for which certificates of value shall be redeemable under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t45/s746"},"text":"section 746 of this title","children":[],"tail":", the series B preferred stock and the common stock conveyed to the Secretary under section 1107 "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002078"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002078"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title shall be deemed to be without fair market value unless in a proceeding brought under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t45/s1105/a/4"},"text":"section 1105(a)(4) of this title","children":[],"tail":" the special court shall have determined that such securities had a value and shall have entered a judgment against the United States for that value. In such an event, the securities shall for purposes of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t45/s746"},"text":"section 746 of this title","children":[],"tail":" be deemed to have that value found by the special court."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id27f3a56e-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tXI/s1167/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title XI, § 1167(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/686"},"text":"95 Stat. 686","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id27f3a56f-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id27f3a570-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id27f3a571-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t45/s1107"},"text":"Section 1107 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/509/tIV/s4033/c/1/C/i/I"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–509, title IV, § 4033(c)(1)(C)(i)(I)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/1908"},"text":"100 Stat. 1908","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id27f3a572-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of subsec. (b) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/s1167"},"text":"section 1167 of Pub. L. 97–35","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (a) of section 1167 amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t45/s743"},"text":"section 743 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (c) of section 1167, which was set out as subsec. (b) of this section and which provided that the clerk of the special court convey to the Secretary certain series B preferred stock and common stock of Conrail on deposit with the court, and authorized the Secretary to hold and exercise all rights to such Conrail securities, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/509/tIV/s4033/c/1/C/i/IV"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–509, title IV, § 4033(c)(1)(C)(i)(IV)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/1908"},"text":"100 Stat. 1908","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
